---

<section class="bg-darkgrey">
    <div class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-6 font-body">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-8 lg:mb-12">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-bold text-white">
                Tailored for the best experience
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-5 font-light sm:text-xl text-gray-400">
                At vintedbot, we specialize in providing the best item tracking
                solution. Our bot ensures fast and efficient tracking,
                guaranteeing profitable results.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div
            class="space-y-8 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-6 xl:gap-10 lg:space-y-0"
